rows.label: qst201607_msg0001
rows.name: ...I knew I couldn't do it.

rows.label: qst201607_msg0002
rows.name: Aww, that's a shame, mo...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0003
rows.name: ...I'm sorry. I quit...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0004
rows.name: Huh? What are you saying, mo?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0005
rows.name:
The stage performance was a
failure, but the concert itself
was a huge success, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0007
rows.name:
Nanakoori-san's song, even just
a part of it, moved people...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0008
rows.name:
And your lovely, shy
personality captured the
hearts of the audience, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0009
rows.name: ...Is that so?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0010
rows.name: It is, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0011
rows.name:
As proof, a fan club called
the Nanakoori Protection Squad
was formed instantly, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0013
rows.name: You did it, Nanakoori, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0014
rows.name:
There were some ups and downs,
but all's well that ends well.

rows.label: qst201607_msg0015
rows.name:
So, Nanakoori, are you
happy, even a little?

rows.label: qst201607_msg0016
rows.name: ...Um, I'm not really sure yet...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0017
rows.name:
But having everyone listen to my
song... I was a little happy...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0018
rows.name:
That's it, mo! That feeling
is what's important, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0019
rows.name:
If you can convey that feeling
to everyone, the next concert
is sure to be a success, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0020
rows.name: My feelings... to everyone...

rows.label: qst201607_msg0021
rows.name:
Now, let's have more
lessons for tomorrow, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0022
rows.name: ...Yes!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0023
rows.name:
This time, let's train each
skill to level 4, mo!

rows.label: qst201607_msg0024
rows.name:
With a solid foundation,
confidence will follow. You
won't be as nervous on stage, mo.
